{"tid":2059102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安倍晉三擬於G7帶頭就「港區國安法」發聲明","createTime":"2020-06-10T15:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T15:44:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3fb288febe9d82debbbc161f96c1555a0b9a073","tid":2059102,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"日本首相安倍晉三在國會指，計劃牽頭在七國集團就北京計劃在香港實施「港區國安法」發表聯合聲明，認為七國集團有領導全球輿論的使命。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩指，對安倍晉三的言論表示嚴重關切，強調香港事務屬中國內政，外國政府不容干涉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531346-20200610.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531346-20200610.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=29676124\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531346-20200610.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a2aaeb20\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531346-20200610.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5e315af3a4f2a1cf9eaa0c828f92b7c58474be0b","tid":2059102,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"圍堵中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0150574417e707c8d2e336c1e3b5bacd6ba705","tid":2059102,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"中共咁大個春袋唔係唔錫呀嘛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d42117722e39271b395f9c4f7995c725acb8d399","tid":2059102,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"梗喺啦<br />\n美國大哥出到聲有乜可能唔做嘢<br />\n喺驚班歐盟左膠累事 <br />\n尤其是Merkel"},{"pid":"e1ce3dce1b85418f60dc0f1105f5ca53db0d5643","tid":2059102,"uid":266342,"like"